Comparar 4 histogramas en 2x2

layout(matrix(c(1,2,3,4), 2, 2, byrow=TRUE))
hist(u_1m, main="1M", col="coral")
hist(u_2m, main="2M", col="lightblue")
hist(u_3m, main="3M", col="lightgreen") 
hist(u_4m, main="4M", col="plum")

plot(density(u_1m), col="red", main="ComparaciÃ³n de Densidades", lwd=2)
lines(density(u_2m), col="blue", lwd=2)
lines(density(u_3m), col="green", lwd=2)
lines(density(u_4m), col="purple", lwd=2)
legend("topright", c("1M","2M","3M","4M"), col=c("red","blue","green","purple"), lwd=2)
